The paper presents a novel framework for introducing declarative knowledge to neural network architectures in order to guide training and prediction. The tasks evaluated in the experiments are related to natural language processing and computer vision, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.NE, and cs.CV. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
